message: Add very basic README.md file. Would still need to check that all defaults and parameter data types etc. are stated correctly there.

Add getting started instructions to README.md. Not quite finished yet. May have to consider leaving the README.md of this package much smaller and creating a separate repo for setting up the whole system. Call it Kestrel, for example.

Use VehicleGpsPosition for location and heading (this topic includes both - VehicleGlobalPosition does not have heading). Note that in VehcileGpsPosition the lat and lon are provided as integers in 1E-7 degrees. This commit also updates README.md and config.yml for relevant parts. Not yet tested.
Swap gps position for a combination of local and global position. Tested with gps position but for some reason the heading value there was NaN while it worked earlier with local position.

1. Refactor initial_guess param to be a list instead of two separate parameters. 2. Get rid of the config arg for the node and use the params file like a ROS params file should be used (had to move Superglue config here too even though not ideal).

1. Move main method to __main__.py. 2. Put matching logic into a separate submodule and create an abstract KeypointMatcher interface - makes it easier to swap matching algorithms in the future. The matching adapter is dynamically loaded based on configuration in YAML file. 3. Remove directory tree from README.md file - annoying to maintain.

Update documentation to use dockerized mapserver instead of mapproxy. Also edits the config/typhoon_h480__ksql_airport.yaml file for mapserver (ideally should not need to change this whether mapproxy or mapserver is used).

Remove WITH_GISNAV build arg from README example. Not needed after multi-stage builds introduced in https://github.com/hmakelin/gisnav-docker/pull/8

Create new autopilots module and implement adapters for PX4 microRTPS and ArduPilot MAVROS ROS bridges. The ArduPilot adapter does not yet implement the gimbal attitude properties so a new configurable static nadir facing camera assumption was introduced along with an example typhoon_h480__ksql_airport_ardupilot.yaml parameter configuration which should be used when running SITL with ArduPilot.
Change old obsolete reference to px4-sitl to just sitl.
Add links to prebuilt images in README.md.
